{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                    // hydrogen // schema // geometry // nurbs"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Nurbs — Non-Uniform Rational B-Splines for professional curve modeling."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | NURBS are the gold standard for precise curve and surface representation"},{"LineComment":" | in CAD, professional animation, and industrial design. They extend B-splines"},{"LineComment":" | with two key features:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Weights**: Each control point has a weight that affects how strongly"},{"LineComment":" |   it \"pulls\" the curve. Weights enable exact representation of conic"},{"LineComment":" |   sections (circles, ellipses, hyperbolas)."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Non-uniform knots**: The knot vector can have non-uniform spacing,"},{"LineComment":" |   allowing finer control over where the curve \"responds\" to control points."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Mathematical Foundation"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | A NURBS curve of degree p is defined as:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" | C(u) = Σᵢ (Nᵢ,ₚ(u) · wᵢ · Pᵢ) / Σᵢ (Nᵢ,ₚ(u) · wᵢ)"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Where:"},{"LineComment":" | - Pᵢ are control points"},{"LineComment":" | - wᵢ are weights (positive numbers)"},{"LineComment":" | - Nᵢ,ₚ(u) are B-spline basis functions of degree p"},{"LineComment":" | - The knot vector determines the basis functions"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Key Properties"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Exact conics**: Circles, ellipses, and arcs can be represented exactly"},{"LineComment":" | - **Local control**: Moving one point affects only nearby curve segments"},{"LineComment":" | - **Affine invariance**: Transformations apply to control points only"},{"LineComment":" | - **Variation diminishing**: The curve is \"smoother\" than control polygon"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Use Cases"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - CAD/CAM systems (Solidworks, AutoCAD, Rhino)"},{"LineComment":" | - Typography and font design"},{"LineComment":" | - Aircraft and automotive body design"},{"LineComment":" | - Professional 3D modeling (professional 3D modeling software)"},{"LineComment":" | - CNC machining tool paths"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This is a leader module that re-exports from submodules:"},{"LineComment":" | - `Nurbs.Types` — Core type definitions"},{"LineComment":" | - `Nurbs.Construction` — Curve constructors"},{"LineComment":" | - `Nurbs.Evaluation` — Point and derivative evaluation"},{"LineComment":" | - `Nurbs.Operations` — Modification, geometry, conversion"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[93,4],"start":[87,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Nurbs","Construction"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[102,4],"start":[95,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Nurbs","Evaluation"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,4],"start":[104,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Nurbs","Operations"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,4],"start":[75,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Nurbs","Types"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,4],"start":[57,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Nurbs"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Nurbs.purs","reExports":{"Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Nurbs.Construction":["nurbsArc","nurbsCircle","nurbsCurve","nurbsEllipse","nurbsFromPoints"],"Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Nurbs.Evaluation":["nurbsCurvatureAt","nurbsNormalAt","nurbsParameterRange","nurbsPointAt","nurbsTangentAt","sampleNurbs"],"Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Nurbs.Operations":["blendNurbsWeights","elevateDegree","insertKnot","isValidNurbs","nurbsBoundingBox","nurbsBoundingBoxViaBeziers","nurbsControlPointAt","nurbsLength","nurbsLengthViaBeziers","nurbsToBeziers","nurbsWeightAt","setControlPoint","setWeight"],"Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Nurbs.Types":["ControlPoint","NurbsCurve","controlPointPosition","controlPointWeight","nurbsControlPoints","nurbsDegree","nurbsKnots","nurbsOrder"]},"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,4],"start":[57,1]}}